Simple Use:
- docker run -p 80:80 -v /path/to/source/code:/var/www/html -d diksy/apache2-php7

Custom Apache2 Config:
- docker run -p 80:80 -v /path/to/source/code:/var/www/html -v /path/to/apache2/config:/etc/apache2/sites-enabled -d diksy/apache2-php7
- docker run -p 80:80 -v /path/to/source/code:/var/www/html -v /path/to/files:/var/www/files -v /path/to/apache2/config:/etc/apache2/sites-enabled -d diksy/apache2-php7

